title: A New Upscale Apartment in Frisco**Washer/Dryer Inc**
posting_body: A New Luxury and Chic Apartment Community In Frisco with Easy Access to The Dallas Tollway.
Dining, Shopping, and Entertainment Close By.
Enjoy the Luxury of Granite Countertops, a Side by Side Refrigerator, Farm Sink, and Stainless Steel Appliances in the Kitchen.
Wood Floors, Walk-In Closets, Mud Room, Garden Tubs, with Washer and Dryer Included in Your Luxury Apartment Home.
Amenities Include a Sports Simulator, a Gorgeous Resort Style Swimming Pool, State of the Art Fitness Center, Walking and Biking Trails, Pet Park, and a Pet Care Station for Your Furry Friend.
